    "Dr. Peter S. Ruckman": "The RSV made it \u201cAT ADAM\u201d (referring to the town in Josh. 3:16), following the blind lead of Moffatt\u2019s translation.\n1980. The RSV [v_Jos_3_16] made it \u201cAT ADAM\u201d (referring to the town in Josh. 3:16), following the blind lead of Moffatt\u2019s translation."
